%N A014978 Inverse of 969th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A014978 Periodic with period length 969. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A014978 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A014978/b014978.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%H A014978 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 969.
